  "key": "A minor",
  "genre": [
    "Alternative",
    "Indie"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 6,
  "lyrics": "Yeah, now it's so far, now it's just so far away All we ever wanna be, yeah, gone today I knew you'd take it all from me I knew you'd be the downfall of me But I still stayed, and I still loved Every second of your hypocrisy So you can go and run and don't get it gone And I can stay here and be sorry, but it won't be long Is there more love to give? Yeah, even though It seems so far away Oh, far away It seems so far away Like the light that was yesterday In this darkness I'll hold still And I fade away Now I find a way to hurt myself And the signs are not my disguises And I know you wanna be here with me But you're far away Too far away It's just too far away From everything, everything that we wanted to say All lost in the light I've been there for any other person But the thing that's inside of you You dream that you're not here But that's still so far away Far away If you wanna give up now Take the easy way Life will still be far away Far away It's all so easy to get carried away And not remember this life But don't teach me to die here Don't teach me to not have that love inside of me And watch out for your own perception of hate All this negativity just dies And makes you far away from yourself And you can't hold down anything like your recourse All your answers, everything They put their hard work in You fumble here Far away from me You scream in the night And I can tell you it's not alright It's just all far away",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 18.940000534057617,
      "text": "Yeah, now it's so far, now it's just so far away",
      "start": 11.140000343322754
    },
    {
      "end": 23.739999771118164,
      "text": "All we ever wanna be, yeah, gone today",
      "start": 19.399999618530273
    },
    {
      "end": 26.600000381469727,
      "text": "I knew you'd take it all from me",
      "start": 23.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 29.979999542236328,
      "text": "I knew you'd be the downfall of me",
      "start": 26.600000381469727
    },
    {
      "end": 32.380001068115234,
      "text": "But I still stayed, and I still loved",
      "start": 29.979999542236328
    },
    {
      "end": 35.08000183105469,
      "text": "Every second of your hypocrisy",
      "start": 32.380001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 37.70000076293945,
      "text": "So you can go and run and don't get it gone",
      "start": 35.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 41.540000915527344,
      "text": "And I can stay here and be sorry, but it won't be long",
      "start": 37.70000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 44.58000183105469,
      "text": "Is there more love to give? Yeah, even though",
      "start": 41.540000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 47.7599983215332,
      "text": "It seems so far away",
      "start": 44.7599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 50.279998779296875,
      "text": "Oh, far away",
      "start": 48.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 53.040000915527344,
      "text": "It seems so far away",
      "start": 50.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 55.36000061035156,
      "text": "Like the light that was yesterday",
      "start": 53.040000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 58.02000045776367,
      "text": "In this darkness I'll hold still",
      "start": 55.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 61.040000915527344,
      "text": "And I fade away",
      "start": 58.02000045776367
    },
    {
      "end": 64.12000274658203,
      "text": "Now I find a way to hurt myself",
      "start": 61.34000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 66.5,
      "text": "And the signs are not my disguises",
      "start": 64.12000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 69.76000213623047,
      "text": "And I know you wanna be here with me",
      "start": 66.5
    },
    {
      "end": 72.05999755859375,
      "text": "But you're far away",
      "start": 69.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 75.04000091552734,
      "text": "Too far away",
      "start": 72.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 77.87999725341797,
      "text": "It's just too far away",
      "start": 75.04000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 82.05999755859375,
      "text": "From everything, everything that we wanted to say",
      "start": 77.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 83.80000305175781,
      "text": "All lost in the light",
      "start": 82.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 86.27999877929688,
      "text": "I've been there for any other person",
      "start": 83.80000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 88.36000061035156,
      "text": "But the thing that's inside of you",
      "start": 86.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 90.41999816894531,
      "text": "You dream that you're not here",
      "start": 88.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 94.91999816894531,
      "text": "But that's still so far away",
      "start": 90.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 97.55999755859375,
      "text": "Far away",
      "start": 96.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 101.73999786376953,
      "text": "If you wanna give up now",
      "start": 99.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 103.72000122070312,
      "text": "Take the easy way",
      "start": 101.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 108.04000091552734,
      "text": "Life will still be far away",
      "start": 103.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 110.80000305175781,
      "text": "Far away",
      "start": 109.19999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 115.26000213623047,
      "text": "It's all so easy to get carried away",
      "start": 110.80000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 116.91999816894531,
      "text": "And not remember this life",
      "start": 115.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 119.18000030517578,
      "text": "But don't teach me to die here",
      "start": 116.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 122.9800033569336,
      "text": "Don't teach me to not have that love inside of me",
      "start": 119.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 126.05999755859375,
      "text": "And watch out for your own perception of hate",
      "start": 122.9800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 128.8000030517578,
      "text": "All this negativity just dies",
      "start": 126.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 131.52000427246094,
      "text": "And makes you far away from yourself",
      "start": 129.4199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 134.8000030517578,
      "text": "And you can't hold down anything like your recourse",
      "start": 131.52000427246094
    },
    {
      "end": 137.17999267578125,
      "text": "All your answers, everything",
      "start": 134.8000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 138.9600067138672,
      "text": "They put their hard work in",
      "start": 137.17999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 140.24000549316406,
      "text": "You fumble here",
      "start": 138.9600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 142.6199951171875,
      "text": "Far away from me",
      "start": 140.25999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 144,
      "text": "You scream in the night",
      "start": 142.6199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 145.9600067138672,
      "text": "And I can tell you it's not alright",
      "start": 144
    },
    {
      "end": 149.9199981689453,
      "text": "It's just all far away",
      "start": 146.5800018310547
    }
  ],
